<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='433304' id='t-433304'>and we made these designs together</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='434908' id='t-434908'>with the local store owners, 
the building owners,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='437521' id='t-437521'>and a team of about a dozen 
young men and women.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='442459' id='t-442459'>They were hired, and then
