<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='454340' id='t-454340'>(Applause)</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='460142' id='t-460142'>And at the end, the city of Philadelphia</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='463765' id='t-463765'>thanked every single one of them</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='465778' id='t-465778'>and gave them a merit for
their accomplishment.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 8:00
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='469094' id='t-469094'>JK: So now we had painted a whole street.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='472246' id='t-472246'>How about we do this whole hill now?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='475801' id='t-475801'>We started looking for funding,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='477679' id='t-477679'>but instead, we just ran into questions,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='480920' id='t-480920'>like, how many houses 
