<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='484339' id='t-484339'>How many square meters is that?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='486495' id='t-486495'>How much paint are you going to use,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='488546' id='t-488546'>and how many people are you going to employ?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='491189' id='t-491189'>And we did try for years to write plans</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='493900' id='t-493900'>for the funding and answer 
