<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='516263' id='t-516263'>you can let the project grow organically</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='518231' id='t-518231'>and have a life of its own.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 8:52
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='521719' id='t-521719'>DU: So what we did is</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='523931' id='t-523931'>we decided to take this 
plan and strip it away</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='527140' id='t-527140'>from all the numbers</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='529030' id='t-529030'>and all the ideas and presumptions</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='530999' id='t-530999'>and just go back to the base idea,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='533362' id='t-533362'>which was to transform this hill</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='535364' id='t-535364'>into a giant work of art.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='537805' id='t-537805'>And instead of looking for funding,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='540207' id='t-540207'>we started a crowdfunding campaign,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='543097' id='t-543097'>and in a little over a month,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='544680' id='t-544680'>more than 1,500 people put together</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='546852' id='t-546852'>and donated over 100,000 dollars.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='550127' id='t-550127'>So for us, this was an amazing 
