<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='553730' id='t-553730'>(Applause) —</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='557246' id='t-557246'>because now we finally had the freedom</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='560295' id='t-560295'>to use all the lessons that we had learned</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='562466' id='t-562466'>and create a project that was built</span>
