<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='571703' id='t-571703'>JK: So we went back, 
and we employed Angelo,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='574800' id='t-574800'>and he's a local artist from Vila Cruzeiro,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='576722' id='t-576722'>very talented guy, and he
